---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Resources"
  description="Application resources and writing examples from Shengmiao Jin for students preparing graduate school applications."
>
  <section class="page-header shell">
    <p class="eyebrow">Resources</p>
    <h1>Application Resources</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      I made these materials public because I remember how confusing the Ph.D.
      application process felt. Please use them as references, not templates to copy directly.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section--tight shell">
    <div class="prose">
      <section>
        <h2>Statement of Purpose</h2>
        <div class="resource-frame">
          <iframe
            src="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1qEUsuVk-SDJ-MNuQIMvue-GRed0Lpp--y4NKLhLYCb4/preview"
            title="Statement of Purpose preview"
            loading="lazy"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Personal Statement</h2>
        <div class="resource-frame">
          <iframe
            src="https://docs.google.com/document/d/13wG9AAamYbZLhOpemyWBkm5WF1TjdbA54uM9rUaHZ2A/preview"
            title="Personal Statement preview"
            loading="lazy"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Inquiry Email Template</h2>
        <p>
          This is a starting point for a short, specific research inquiry. The strongest
          version should explain why that professor's work connects to your own experience.
        </p>
        <pre class="template">Dear Professor [Full Name],

My name is [Your Name]. I am currently [your current role/program], and my research interests are [brief research interests]. I am writing to express my interest in pursuing a Ph.D. under your guidance.

My past research spans [area 1], [area 2], and [area 3]. In particular, I worked on [specific project], where I [one concrete contribution]. This experience made me especially interested in [research direction].

[A short paragraph on how the professor's recent work connects to your interests. Mention one specific paper, project, or idea.]

I attached my CV to help you better understand my background. You can also find more about my work at [website link]. Thank you for your time and consideration.

Sincerely,
[Your Name]</pre>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
